Including <code>text</code>, <code>password</code>, <code>email</code>, <code>number</code>, <code>date</code>, <code>datetime-local</code>, <code>week</code>, <code>month</code>, <code>tel</code>, <code>url</code>, <code>search</code>, <code>time</code><!----><!----></p> <p><!---->For <code>checkbox</code>, <code>radio</code>, <code>file</code>, <code>range</code> use their own class names, as they are not visually input fields.<!----><!----></p> <p><!---->Inputs can be used with <code>validator</code> class to have validation styles. <a href="/components/validator/">See Validator component</a> for more details.<!----><!----></p> <div class="component-preview not-prose text-base-content my-6 lg:my-12" id="text-input-with-data-list-suggestion"><!--[--><div class="flex
